facts.fact_text: Vietnam's industrial production surged 21.5% year-on-year in January 2025.

evidences.evidence_text: Vietnam’s industrial production surged 21.5% year-on-year in January 2025

facts.fact_text: The 21.5% increase marks the fastest growth since April 2021.

facts.fact_text: Manufacturing output grew by 23.6% in January 2025, compared to 10.9% in December.

evidences.evidence_text: Output growth strengthened across most sectors, including manufacturing (23.6% vs 10.9% in December)

facts.fact_text: Electricity and gas supply increased by 14.1% in January 2025, compared to 11.2% in December.
Water supply, waste management, and wastewater treatment grew by 13.6% in January 2025, compared to 6.3% in December.

facts.fact_text: Mining and quarrying picked up sharply to 10.3% in January 2025, compared to 0.2% in December.

facts.fact_text: On a monthly basis, industrial output edged down 0.2% in January 2025.
